# Helmet Violation Detection System

A real-time helmet violation detection system using YOLOv8, Streamlit, and PaddleOCR.

This application detects:
- Motorcyclists not wearing helmets within a defined zone
- Automatically captures and logs number plates of violators

---

## Features

- Live video detection via webcam or uploaded video
- Helmet and number plate detection using YOLOv8
- Number plate recognition using PaddleOCR
- Custom polygonal detection zone
- Fine logging with:
  - Vehicle number
  - Date and time
  - Snapshot of number plate
- Export fines as CSV
- Preview of all captured number plate images

---

## Interface (Streamlit)

- Sidebar: Violation history
- Main View:
  - Live or uploaded video feed
  - Fine log table
  - Captured plate images
  - Download CSV button

---

## Installation

Requires Python 3.8 or higher.

### 1. Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/helmet-fine-detection.git
cd helmet-fine-detection
